Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙的目的是讓七鄉開花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.59,0:00:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在為止都單獨行動的圓神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟一些棘手的人聯合起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.09,0:00:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屠龍者 吸血鬼獵人 驅魔師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有……死靈使
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.82,0:00:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 這個力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.45,0:00:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收回去了 因為那只是我的玩具罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.01,0:02:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殭屍在沒有符札的情況下行動這種情況…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她確實是那麼活動了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之 我先試著調查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.61,0:02:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙終於開始行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.61,0:02:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平和的日常生活也就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.05,0:02:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那一切發生之前 恐怕也沒多少時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們這群傢伙 是吃拉麵的時候嗎 我在講話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很美味呢 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:02:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥你也在吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這麼沒人情味的話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餓著肚子也沒法參戰 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個拉麵 是鈴的新作品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘗嘗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.16,0:03:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 我吃飽了 真是太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托它的福比昨天更有力氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.79,0:03:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉告下鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新作 很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級美味 好吃到爆耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.81,0:03:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 差不多到巡邏的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先從一丁目開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在辦公室查些資料
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我鬆口氣 翹班… 啊疼～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉要多工作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦 剛剛吃完拉麵嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 被教訓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:03:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…小姬他們已經回去了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 區長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那個死靈使是鈴的老相識的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想好好跟她談談話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把他揪到這裡來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幸福呀 鈴那小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到人類和妖怪兩方保護的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不多見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我跟八重不一樣 不會出手相助的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 請稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打聽情報什麼的我不會聽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉麵七人份 4900日元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 別跑……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石榴…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是個玩具而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.21,0:06:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要睡到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開主人 來到這麼遠的地方 真是個壞孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來保護你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你想要的東西已經到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷窺麼 真是不好的癖好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和屍體做朋友恐怕也談不上什麼好癖好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼～少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做足情報費的份是不行的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為契約 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 先把這個交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 工作會給你做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以最好別出手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.37,0:07:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 三丁目也無異常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…哪個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個的話～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.61,0:08:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～姬～ 鈴被帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茱莉姐讓我告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:09:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢～可沒這份閒心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後會帶回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫恭助 別跟丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就稍微陪你 玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻新鎮 鎮長 槍櫻姬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做石榴 狂卷石榴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很強嘛 真的很強
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 無聊的很～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪強是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個鎮還有更加有趣的傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作的時候 要叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮長～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雲切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪打
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 已經解決了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 是呀 太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪獵人絕不會只有這點程度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在特定條件下會變成壓倒性的強悍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是妖怪獵人對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說我 我自身不強也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死靈使
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操縱玩具才是我的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清醒一點 鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許把我們的鎮民叫做玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮 秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.92,0:13:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真 太天真了 你還嫩著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒屍體的話 做一個不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速生長 提早死亡的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操作死體和屍鬼才是死靈使的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.03,0:13:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的特定條件下…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 姬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:13:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 打擊本體的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是無趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼蠻力的話 可是贏不了我的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牆壁～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是有嘛 有趣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半妖 人類和妖怪各半的墮落的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.14,0:14:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一樣的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把我跟你扯到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉原本的自己去傷害他人的你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:15:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 相同的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡最與眾不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自於你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 不錯嘛 放馬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺掉我的話 你就算不想聽也會知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己也是個怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你也要有這個能力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉 來點什麼長的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,short cut 長戟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼危險的東西 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是殺掉的話就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:16:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不殺生 此刻言葉在這裡 也多虧了這個信念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就先懲罰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再教育
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後再讓她說「對不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 茱莉 未免太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條路沒錯吧 小藍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對的 河岸 向河岸前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這些東西 到底幹什麼用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丟下我～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 那個啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強 真的好強
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一對一的話還我是比較強的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一對多的話 她就比我強哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有如此程度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱 很熱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量不停的不停的湧出來 身體要融化了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要拍怪獸電影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很快嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,short cut
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.43,0:17:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,short cut
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,short cut
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錘子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,針
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,short cut 汽油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.08,0:18:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噠噠噠噠噠噠噠噠噠噠…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操縱這個怪物的原理跟我的身體一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.22,0:18:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念誦行動指令 傳達到神經中 讓各個部分都受到刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生物電流 那就是你的弱點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.43,0:19:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茱莉姐 接下來就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫院感謝你喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.17,0:19:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,short cut 貫通炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做東鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特技是料理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的食物是餃子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 散步也很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.87,0:19:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭的東西是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.33,0:20:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿星的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來保護你 因為我也是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再輕一些 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,料理 第一次做是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.90,0:20:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 搞不好比我還厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:20:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那麼 如果記住了各種各樣的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以幫我試吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.14,0:21:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.19,0:21:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩…害怕夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直一個人在逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不死之身 晚上也睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夜空下面的話 又會～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始 這裡就是你的家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡有屋頂呀 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.03,0:21:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.80,0:21:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:22:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 石榴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.01,0:22:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要救我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.74,0:22:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～因為我也是一個人嘛 也許
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.58,0:22:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.86,0:22:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然表面上說「我來保護你」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.86,0:22:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是我自己想要被保護呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.45,0:22:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石榴…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.91,0:22:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人的話 就不會孤獨了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.50,0:22:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.90,0:22:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.97,0:22:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.94,0:22:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石榴…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.96,0:22:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.67,0:23:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那群欺負你的人統統殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.25,0:23:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.23,0:23:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.54,0:23:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.69,0:23:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不賴嘛 死靈使
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.65,0:23:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這種對手 不用玩具也可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.60,0:23:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.79,0:23:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.74,0:23:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 石榴 快住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.76,0:23:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想要帶你回去而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓回跑掉的寵物是飼主的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.40,0:23:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.86,0:23:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寵物什麼的 玩具什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.74,0:23:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會把鈴交給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.01,0:23:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快滾出這個鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.57,0:23:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我今天逃回去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.57,0:23:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管幾次我還會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.75,0:23:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那時我會讓這個鎮留下一些傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.46,0:24:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法磨滅的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.15,0:24:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴 來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.61,0:24:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.91,0:24:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.11,0:24:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬和朋友們 還有寶寶蘭的老闆娘 店主大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.20,0:24:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有鎮上的其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.59,0:24:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這兩年中我非常快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.77,0:24:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 石榴卻是一直孤獨一人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.84,0:24:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個溫柔的對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.22,0:24:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個說我做的飯很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.94,0:24:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個在有屋頂的家中迎接我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.46,0:24:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是石榴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.64,0:24:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟石榴一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.46,0:25:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石榴 住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.70,0:25:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.00,0:25:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.56,0:25:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 兩個人一起生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.92,0:25:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.30,0:25:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個力量
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.26,0:25:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圓神
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.75,0:26:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這個鎮子的人口有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.34,0:26:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2040人 到現在為止
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.52,0:26:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈哈 那可真是不錯 那可真是不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.32,0:26:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始 我的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.18,0:26:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會達到2040個
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.12,0:26:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可真是不錯呀
