Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:16.24,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}As you like
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.33,0:02:17.17,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}As you like
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:18.64,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}As you like
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.90,0:00:33.18,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}和著心跳 傾聽四重奏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.29,0:00:35.91,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}著迷其中 吟唱四重奏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.96,0:00:39.84,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}我在做什麼 你可以隨你心意的盡情猜想
